- HRT Log
  - Current clock (optional seconds)
  - Date entry + calendar popup
  - Time entry
  - Optional short title for entry
  - Multiple medication rows (name, dose, unit, time, route)
  - "+ Add medication" and per-row "Remove"
  - Medication suggestions dropdown
  - Unit / Route dropdowns, "Now" button fills time
  - Mood dropdown, Symptoms single-line, Notes multi-line (adjustable font)
  - Save Entry (validates at least one medication)
  - Quick focus on date field when shown

- History
  - Search box (search across fields)
  - Start / End date filters
  - Filter / Clear / Refresh / Export filtered entries
  - Scrollable list of entries (timestamp + title/med)
  - Detailed view of selected entry (medications, fields)
  - Delete entry (with optional confirm)
  - Duplicate entry
  - Ctrl+F focus shortcut support

- Resources
  - Scrollable list of saved resources
  - New / Delete resource
  - Editor: Title, Link/contact, Tags, Notes
  - Save Resource
  - Open Link (auto-adds http:// when appropriate)

- Settings
  - Inclusive language toggle
  - Appearance (System/Light/Dark) and color theme
  - Editable lists: Regimens, Routes, Units (add, delete, reorder)
  - Default unit / default route pickers
  - Date format and Time format pickers
  - Toggles: confirm destructive actions, show seconds, backup on save
  - Window size, Notes font size slider
  - Save Settings / Reset to defaults
  - Applies theme and window geometry (snaps to monitor)

- Help
  - Full inline help & guide text explaining pages and behavior
  - Data file locations and troubleshooting tips
  - Keyboard shortcuts list

- Report a Bug
  - One-line summary field
  - Editable bug-report template prefilled with environment info
  - Copy template to clipboard
  - Open Gmail compose with prefilled subject/body
  - Save report locally (stores in JSON)
  - Clear/reset template

- Contribute
  - Contribution plan / notes textbox
  - Save plan locally (stores in JSON)
  - Open GitHub link

- App / Global features
  - Per-user JSON storage for entries, resources, settings, bugs, contributions
  - Optional .bak backups on save
  - Keyboard shortcuts: Ctrl+1..7 (pages), Left/Right (cycle pages), Ctrl+S (context-aware save), Ctrl+F
  - Status bar for transient messages
  - Snap window geometry to monitor under cursor
  - Safe reload/apply theme and settings, robust error handling